            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "A xanthos can sense the alignment of stellar objects (asteroids, comets, planets, and so on), which form conjunctions that grant them magical travel. During these conjunctions, the xanthos can use their teleport spell-like ability as <i>interplanetary teleport</i> to reach any world they have visited before, or as <i>plane shift</i> to reach any plane. These conjunctions occur at the GM\u2019s discretion and usually remain viable for 10d10 hours, after which it could be days, weeks, or even months before another conjunction occurs.",
